\n    <tr>\n      <td>£21,000 and under</td>\n      <td>No repayments</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>£25,000</td>\n      <td>£30</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>£30,000</td>\n      <td>£67</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>£40,000</td>\n      <td>£142</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>£50,000</td>\n      <td>£217</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>£60,000</td>\n      <td>£292</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>Once you&rsquo;re registered with Student Finance England you can <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://signin.slc.co.uk/pls/orasso/slc_login.oaupk002.p_get_username?site2pstoretoken=v1.2~168B0E4C~D224D3BE3885DE3AD58C853F95CAAEB6455DD930D171DEAD5270642D37276BB7C26D768CDF7972CA89027B188026ADA3AD5DE41CD5C51CA663EA09C8871318BC8480781D233EDEB50B5D0E31729\" title=\"check your student finance balance online\">check your balance online</a></p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>If your course finishes before 2016, repayments won’t start until April 2016.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>If you leave the UK, repayments are based on the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.studentloanrepayment.co.uk/pls/portal/docs/PAGE/RPIPG001/RPIPS001/RPIPS006/DG_200469.PDF\" title=\"EU students earnings thresholds (PDF, 240KB)\">earnings threshold (PDF, 240KB)</a> for the country where you live.</p>\n\n<h2>Interest on your student loans</h2>\n<p>You pay interest from the time your first payment is made until you pay your loan back in full. </p>\n\n<p>If your course started before 1 September 2012 <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.studentloanrepayment.co.uk/portal/page?_pageid=93,6678642&amp;_dad=portal&amp;_schema=PORTAL\" title=\"interest rates for courses before September 2012\">different rules apply.</a></p>\n\n<p>For courses that started on or after 1 September 2012 the following interest rates apply:</p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Income</th>\n      <th>Interest rate</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>W