y for student finance</h2>\n\n<p>You have to apply every year. You need your passport details the first time you apply. Don&rsquo;t send your UK passport.</p>\n\n<p>Only <abbr title=\"European Union\">EU</abbr> students have to send their passport or identity card.  </p>\n\n<p>You can apply up to 9 months after the start of your course.</p>\n\n<p>About 6 weeks after your online application you&rsquo;ll get a declaration form in the post. Sign this and send it back. </p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Student</th>\n      <th>Application form</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>UK full-time students</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/student-finance-register-login &quot;Apply online for student finance&quot;\">Apply online</a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>UK part-time students</td>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.sfengland.slc.co.uk/media/428527/sfe_ptgc_form.pdf\" title=\"Part-time students form (PDF, 402KB)\">Part-time student application form (PDF, 402KB)</a> <br /> <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.sfengland.slc.co.uk/media/426284/sfe_ptci2_1213_v1_4.pdf\" title=\"Part-time student income confirmation form (PDF, 89KB)\">Income confirmation form (PDF, 89KB)</a> <br /> <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.sfengland.slc.co.uk/media/434457/cb1.pdf\" title=\"Part-time student benefits confirmation form (PDF, 265KB)\">Benefits confirmation form (PDF, 265KB)</a> <br /> <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.sfengland.slc.co.uk/media/434454/sfe_co2_1213.pdf\" title=\"Update your details (PDF, 1.5MB)\">Update your details form (PDF, 1.5MB)</a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><abbr title=\"European Union\">EU</abbr> full-time students</td>\n      <td>Existing <abbr title=\"European Union\">EU</abbr> students should use form EUPR1a, which will be sent to them automatically.<br /> <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.sfengland.slc.co.uk/media/420654/euco1.pdf\" title=\"EU update your details (PDF, 141KB)\"><abbr t